DevilDuer looks at Vamprah with a frown on his face as she starts 
screaming. For a second, he thought she was adressing him, but his 
name wasn't Darkfate.

Seeing her fall back to the floor, he brings Diamond's knife forward 
again, trying to cut the necklace and wondering why Diamond had her 
hand on his shoulder.
